The guitarist and the drummer OWNED this song..... Really a  Soul Rocking Song... Thank you STRINGS and Salman.....Could have been sung by any one but the soul of this Song is your lyrics, production, guitarist, &  drummer..... 

We south asians put tooo much emphasize on a voice of a singer A.K.A Lata M.  but the true talent are the lyricist, producers, and the instrument players.  Look at Bob Dylan the man sounds like a restarted buffalo..... but it don't matter it's his lyrics and music that moves the soul.

Lata and Momina can sing their hearts out but with out you there is no music to sing to....
